game_description: Shooting Practise is designed to improve you aiming skills, so you can survive in Multiplayer Shooter. - Different level, each designed to train another aspect of your aiming skills. - Aiming in generel - Aiming speed by training your reflexes - Trigger speed - Improveingperipheral vision The training sessions are not designed to be fun but they are designed to be efficient.
review_2: This is the best game ever
